===1990年代增長與普及===
到1990年代後期，美國人均醫療衛生支出重新開始增長，在2002年左右達到高峰。<ref name="PWC">[http://www.ahipbelieves.com/media/The%20Factors%20Fueling%20Rising%20Healthcare%20Costs.pdf The Factors Fueling Rising Healthcare Costs 2006] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071127151147/http://www.ahipbelieves.com/media/The%20Factors%20Fueling%20Rising%20Healthcare%20Costs.pdf |date=2007-11-27 }}, report prepared by Price Waterhouse Coopers for [[America's_Health_Insurance_Plans|America's Health Insurance Plans]], January 2006, accessed 2007-10-05</ref>雖然管理式醫療護理要求控制費用，但美國的醫療衛生支出的成長速度仍超過GDP的成長速度，自1970年以來，醫療衛生支出年增長率比GDP快約2.4%。<ref>[http://www.kff.org/insurance/7692.cfm Trends in Health Care Costs and Spending] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kff.org/insurance/7692.cfm |date=20130408012239 }}, Kaiser Family Foundation Health Care Marketplace Project, September 2007, accessed 2007-10-05</ref>
  
然而，根據美國保險行業協會的《{{link-en|美國健康保險計劃|America's Health Insurance Plans}}》，現在有90％的美國醫療保險投保人都登記參加某種形式的管理式醫療護理計劃。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.healthdecisions.org/LearningCenter/Facts.aspx |title=Fast Facts |accessdate=2007-07-18 |work=HealthDecisions.org |publisher=America's Health Insurance Plans |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928204630/http://www.healthdecisions.org/LearningCenter/Facts.aspx |archivedate=2007-09-28 }}</ref>《國家管理式醫療護理組織目錄（The National Directory of Managed Care Organizations）》（第七版）包含有5,279多種計劃<ref>https://www.amazon.ae/National-Directory-Managed-Organizations-Seventh/dp/188236483X</ref>，其中包括新的以消費者為導向的醫療衛生計劃，還有{{link-en|健康儲蓄帳戶|health savings accounts}}。此外，有26個州與管理式醫療護理組織（MCO）簽訂合同，為老年人和殘疾人士提供[[長期照護|長期照護]]。各州向提供全面護理，並自行承擔管理成本風險的MCO，按照[[論人計酬支付|論人計酬支付]]的方式支付費用。<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Agency for Healthcare Research and Quality |url=https://innovations.ahrq.gov/perspectives/states-turn-managed-care-constrain-medicaid-long-term-care-costs |title=States Turn to Managed Care To Constrain Medicaid Long-Term Care Costs |date=2014-04-09 |accessdate=2014-04-14 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006105609/https://innovations.ahrq.gov/perspectives/states-turn-managed-care-constrain-medicaid-long-term-care-costs |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
==技術==
{{see also|[[使用管理|使用管理]]|醫療必要性}}
 
管理式醫療護理最典型的形式是使用醫療衛生提供者的小組或網絡，為登記加入者提供服務。這種集成的系統通常包括以下一項或多項：
*指定的醫生和醫療機構，被稱為提供者網絡，患者受到要求或是鼓勵去利用<ref name="Managed Care 1995, page 9">Managed Care: Integrating the Delivery and Financing of Health Care – Part A, Health Insurance Association of America, 1995, page 9 {{ISBN|1-879143-26-7}}</ref><ref>[http://www.ahipresearch.org/PDFs/ValueSurvey/AllStatesReport.pdf ''The value of provider networks and the role of out-of-network charges in rising health care costs: A survey of charges billed by out-of-network physicians,''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120226080846/http://www.ahipresearch.org/PDFs/ValueSurvey/AllStatesReport.pdf|date=2012-02-26}} [[America's_Health_Insurance_Plans|America's Health Insurance Plans]], August 2009</ref><ref>Gina Kolata, [https://www.nytimes.com/2009/08/12/health/policy/12insure.html "Survey Finds High Fees Common in Medical Care ,"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/08/12/health/policy/12insure.html |date=20210427114418 }} [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]], August 11, 2009</ref><ref>Peter R. Kongstvedt, "The Managed Health Care Handbook," Fourth Edition, Aspen Publishers, Inc., 2001, page 3, {{ISBN|0-8342-1726-0}}</ref><ref name="HIAA Terminology">Margaret E. Lynch, Editor, "Health Insurance Terminology," Health Insurance Association of America, 1992, {{ISBN|1-879143-13-5}}</ref>
*有正式的使用管理和品質改進計劃，包括[[疾病管理|疾病管理]]和{{link-en|病例管理|case management}}
*強調[[預防醫學|預防醫學]]，包括{{link-en|工作場所健康維護|Workplace wellness}}和{{link-en|患者教育|patient education}}
 
這些技術可應用於網絡型的保險計劃，也可供非網絡型者應用。非網絡型的提供者運用管理式醫療護理，有時被稱為"管理式保障"。

===成本分擔===
保險公司提供的{{link-en|高自付額醫療保險計劃|High-deductible health plan}}，會激勵消費者選擇更便宜的醫療衛生提供者，並減少醫療衛生使用，以降低成本。

{{link-en|參考價格|reference price}}計劃是另一種分擔費用的方法，用這種方法，醫療保險公司只支付一定金額，而任何超出部分都由患者自付。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sourceonhealthcare.org/reference-pricing-when-transparency-is-not-enough/|title=Reference Pricing: When Transparency Is Not Enough – The Source on HealthCare Price and Competition|website=sourceonhealthcare.org|language=en-US|access-date=2019-06-04|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428141054/https://sourceonhealthcare.org/reference-pricing-when-transparency-is-not-enough/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
===提供者網絡===
像[[聯合健康集團|聯合健康集團]]這樣的保險機構會定期與提供者進行合同談判；合同經常有終止的可能。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.uhcprovider.com/content/dam/provider/docs/public/admin-guides/UnitedHealthcare_Administrative_Guide_2017.pdf|title=UnitedHealthcare Care Provider Administrative Guide|website=United Healthcare|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125103150/https://www.uhcprovider.com/content/dam/provider/docs/public/admin-guides/UnitedHealthcare_Administrative_Guide_2017.pdf|archive-date=2018-11-25|url-status=dead|access-date=2018-11-25}}</ref>備受矚目的合同糾紛會發生在全國性的提供者網絡身上，例如在2018年，聯合健康集團與一家主要的急診室醫生集團{{link-en|Envision Healthcare|Envision Healthcare}}之間的糾紛。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uhc.com/erfacts|title=Envision and ER Costs {{!}} UnitedHealthcare|website=www.uhc.com|language=en|access-date=2018-11-25|archive-date=2018-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125204036/https://www.uhc.com/erfacts|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
維護最新的醫療衛生提供者目錄有其必要，因為{{link-en|聯邦醫療保險和聯邦醫療補助服務中心|Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services}}（CMS）可對目錄過時的保險公司處以罰款。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://www.healthcarefinancenews.com/news/unitedhealthcare-optum-humana-multiplan-and-quest-diagnostics-launch-blockchain-provider|title=UnitedHealthcare, Optum, Humana, MultiPlan and Quest Diagnostics launch blockchain provider director pilot|website=Healthcare Finance News|language=en|access-date=2018-11-25|archive-date=2018-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125162556/https://www.healthcarefinancenews.com/news/unitedhealthcare-optum-humana-multiplan-and-quest-diagnostics-launch-blockchain-provider|dead-url=no}}</ref>聯合健康集團要求提供者，根據它們加入時的約定，主動把變更通知聯合健康集團，但聯合健康集團還備有專業驗證推廣計劃（Professional Verification Outreach），會主動向提供者要求更新的訊息。<ref name=":2" />而服務提供者也必須維護與其他保險機構的聯繫資訊（例如，與聯合健康集團類似的其他保險集團）。維護這些目錄所花費的總成本估計每年要花21億美金，因此業者於2018年開始引進[[區塊鏈|區塊鏈]]，讓目錄能夠共享，以節約複雜的維護成本。<ref name=":3" />
 
當患者從網絡外的醫生獲得醫療護理時，可能會有{{link-en|差額收費|Balance billing}}發生（如果醫療保險報銷的金額不足，患者必須支付差額）；這在急診或住院護理中尤為常見，在這種情況下，患者可能不會被告知提供者並不在同一網絡之內。<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.healthaffairs.org/do/10.1377/hblog20180924.442050/full/|title=Analyzing New Bipartisan Federal Legislation Limiting Surprise Medical Bills {{!}} Health Affairs|website=www.healthaffairs.org|language=en|doi=10.1377/hblog20180924.442050|access-date=2019-04-16|doi-broken-date=2020-08-24|journal=|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405074936/https://www.healthaffairs.org/do/10.1377/hblog20180924.442050/full/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
===使用管理===
使用管理（UM）或稱使用審查（utilization review）是指使用管理式醫療護理技術，例如[[事先授權|事先授權]]，讓付款人可在提供醫療福利之前，利用循證標準或準則去評估服務的適當性，以便管理成本。UM標準是醫療指南，可在醫療機構內部制定，也可從供應商處獲取，然後加以調整，以適合當地條件。兩種常用的UM標準框架是McKesson InterQual標準<ref>Mitus, A. J. (2008). The birth of InterQual: evidence-based decision support criteria that helped change healthcare. Prof Case Manag, 13(4), 228-233</ref>和MCG（之前稱為Milliman Care Guidelines）<ref>{{cite news|author=Sebastian, Michael|url=http://adage.com/article/media/hearst-rolls-division-hearst-health/291297/|title=Hearst's New Health Division is a Departure from Magazines and TV|date=January 27, 2014|accessdate=April 14, 2018|publisher=[[AdAge|AdAge]]|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428234454/https://adage.com/article/media/hearst-rolls-division-hearst-health/291297|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
  
===法律訴訟===
